\c 25
\s UPawuli umangalelwa phambi kukaFestusi
\p
\v 1 Ngakho kwathi uFestusi esengenile emkhonweni\x + 23.34.\x*, emva kwensuku ezintathu\x + 28.17.\x* wenyukela\x + 25.9. Luka 2.4. Seb. 24.1.\x* eJerusalema esuka eKesariya\x + 25.4,6,13. 8.40.\x*,
\v 2 labapristi abakhulu\x + 24.1.\x* lezikhulu zamaJuda\x + Mark. 6.21.\x* bammangalela uPawuli kuye, bemncenga,
\v 3 bacela ukwenzelwa umusa omelane laye, ukuthi amthume eJerusalema\x + 25.15.\x*\x + 24.1.\x*, becathamela ukumbulala endleleni\x + 23.12-15. 9.24.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa uFestusi waphendula ngokuthi uPawuli ugciniwe eKesariya\x + 25.4,6,13. 8.40.\x*, lokuthi laye ngokwakhe uzakuya \add khona\add* ngokuphangisa.
\v 5 Wathi: Ngakho labo abenelisayo phakathi kwenu kabehle kanye \add lami\add*; uba kukhona ulutho olubi ngaleyondoda, bayimangalele\x + Luka 14.31. Seb. 11.17. 1 Kor. 1.26. Isam. 6.15.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kwathi esehlale phakathi kwabo insuku ezedlula itshumi, wehlela\x + 24. 1.\x* eKesariya\x + 25.4,6,13. 8.40.\x*; kusisa wahlala esihlalweni sokwahlulela\x + 25.10,17. Mat. 27.19.\x* walaya ukuthi uPawuli alethwe.
\v 7 Kwathi esefikile, amaJuda ayehlile evela eJerusalema ema e\add m\add*hanqile\x + 24. 1.\x*, embeka amacala amanengi lanzima uPawuli, ayengelakuwaqinisa\x + 2.22.\x*\x + 24.5,13.\x*,
\v 8 yena eziphendulela \add wathi\x + 25.16. 19.33.\x*\add*: Lemlayweni wamaJuda, lethempelini, lakuKesari kangonanga lutho\x + 21.28. 24.12. 28.17. 6.13.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa uFestusi ethanda ukuthabisa amaJuda\x + 24.27.\x*, waphendula uPawuli wathi: Uyathanda\x + 25.20.\x* yini ukwenyukela eJerusalema\x + 25.9. Luka 2.4. Seb. 24.1.\x*, wahlulelwe khona ngalezizinto phambi kwami?
\v 10 Kodwa uPawuli wathi: Ngimi phambi kwesihlalo sokwahlulela sikaKesari\x + 25.10,17. Mat. 27.19.\x*, lapho okufanele ngahlulelwe khona; kangonanga lutho kumaJuda, njengoba lawe usazi kuhle kakhulu\x + 2 Tim. 1.18.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba uba ngonile ngenze ulutho olufanele ukufa, kangali ukufa\x + 25.25.\x*; kodwa uba kungekho lutho lwezinto abangimangalela ngazo, kakulamuntu onganginikela kubo ngesihle\x + 25.16. 3.14. 27.24. Luka 7.42.\x*. Ngilidlulisela kuKesari\x + 25.12,21,25. 26.32. 28.19.\x*.
\v 12 Khona uFestusi esekhulume lomphakathi waphendula \add wathi\add*: Ulidlulisele kuKesari? KuKesari uzakuya\x + 25.12,21,25. 26.32. 28.19.\x*.
\s UAgripha ubikelwa udaba lukaPawuli
\p
\v 13 Kwathi sekudlule insuku ezithile, uAgripha inkosi loBernike bafika eKesariya\x + 25.4,6,13. 8.40.\x*, ukuze babingelele uFestusi.
\v 14 Kwathi sebehlezi khona insuku ezinengi, uFestusi wayilandisela inkosi izindaba zikaPawuli\x + Gal. 2.2.\x*, esithi: Kukhona indoda ethile eyatshiywa nguFelike iyisibotshwa\x + 24.27.\x*,
\v 15 kwathi ngiseJerusalema\x + 25.2-6.\x*, abapristi abakhulu labadala bamaJuda bammangalela, becela isigwebo esimelene laye\x + 25.15.\x*.
\v 16 Engabaphendula ngathi: Kakusiwo umkhuba wamaRoma ukumnikela umuntu ekufeni\x + 25.16. 3.14. 27.24. Luka 7.42.\x*, omangalelweyo labammangalelayo benga\add lethwa\add*nga ubuso ngobuso\x + 23.30. 24.19.\x*, njalo azuze ithuba lokuziphendulela ngecala\x + 25.16. 19.33.\x*.
\v 17 Ngakho sebebuthene lapha, kangizange ngiphuze; ngo\add suku\add* olulandelayo\x + 25.2-6.\x* ngahlala esihlalweni sokwahlulela\x + 25.10,17. Mat. 27.19.\x*, ngalaya ukuthi indoda ilethwe;
\v 18 leyo aba\add yi\add*mangalelayo sebemi kabavezanga cala ngayo ngezinto mina ebengizicabangela\x + 25.27. Mat. 27.37. Mark. 15.26.\x*,
\v 19 kodwa babelokuphikisana okuthile laye\x + 18.15. 23.29.\x* ngenkolo yakibo\x + 17.22.\x*, langothile uJesu owafayo, uPawuli othi ngaye uyaphila.
\v 20 Kuthe mina ngisadidekile ngombuzo onje\f + \fk ngisadidekile: \fl kumbe, \fq ngisadidekile ukuthi ngibuze njani ngakho.\f*, ngathi, angathanda yini ukuya eJerusalema\x + 25.9.\x*, ayekwahlulelwa khona ngalezozinto.
\v 21 Kodwa kwathi uPawuli eselidlulisele phambili ukuthi agcinelwe ukuhlolwa yinkosi enkulu\x + 25.12,21,25. 26.32. 28.19.\x*, ngalaya ukuthi agcinwe, ngize ngimthume kuKesari.
\v 22 UAgripha wasesithi kuFestusi: Lami bengithanda ukuthi ngimuzwe lumuntu. Yena wathi: Kusasa uzamuzwa\x + 9.15.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Ngakho kusisa, kwathi uAgripha loBernike befika ngokuzibonakalisa okukhulu\x + 25.13.\x*, basebengena endlini yokwahlulela kanye lezinduna ezinkulu\x + Mark. 6.21.\x* lamadoda ayizikhulu zomuzi, uFestusi waselaya ukuthi uPawuli alethwe.
\v 24 UFestusi wasesithi: Nkosi Agripha, lani lonke madoda elikhona lapha kanye lathi, liyambona lo elangicela ngaye\x + Roma 11.2.\x* lonke ixuku lamaJuda\x + 25.2,7.\x* eJerusalema kanye lalapha, limemeza \add lisithi\add* kasafanele ukuphila\x + 22.22.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa mina ngathola ukuthi kenzanga lutho olufanele ukufa\x + 23.29. 26.31. 23.9. 25.11.\x*, lokuthi yena\x + 25.11,12.\x* ngokwakhe eselidlulisele enkosini enkulu\x + 25.12,21,25. 26.32. 28.19.\x*, ngaquma ukumthuma.
\v 26 Okungaye kangilalutho oluqinileyo engingalubhalela inkosi. Ngakho ngimlethile phambi kwenu, ikakhulu phambi kwakho, nkosi Agripha, ukuze kuthi esehloliwe ngibe lakho engingakubhala.
\v 27 Ngoba ngibona kungaqondanga ukuthuma isibotshwa, kungatshengiswanga lamacala amelene laso\x + 25.27. Mat. 27.37. Mark. 15.26.\x*.
